STATE EX REL. NAVISTAR, INC.
v.
INDUS. COMM. 2018-1416 Supreme Court of Ohio. August 21, 2019

CASE ANNOUNCEMENT

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULING

Appellant, Navistar, Inc., ordered to show cause within 14 days why its appeal should not be dismissed as moot. Appellees may file a response within seven days of the filing of Navistar's response.
